    "ideation": "The sponge emoji is reimagined as a highly absorbent, squishy character. The animation cycle reflects the physical properties of a sponge: soaking up liquid, becoming heavy and bloated, and then being violently squeezed out. The eyes use scale and gaze to mimic the compression of a porous material—they start airy and light, then bulge as the sponge 'fills,' and finally squint into narrow slits as the 'squeeze' occurs. The mouth acts as the liquid level/surface tension, moving from a gentle ripple to a dense, vibrating wave during the wringing phase. The color palette shifts from a dry, sandy yellow to a deep, saturated gold and finally to a bubbly, aerated white.",
